108
00:06:08,160 --> 00:06:10,549
Didn't we agree to have lunch together?

109
00:06:10,550 --> 00:06:11,829
- What do you want to eat?
- But you said you had an appointment.

110
00:06:11,830 --> 00:06:13,829
