253
00:17:07,830 --> 00:17:08,590
She?

254
00:17:09,190 --> 00:17:10,309
What for?

255
00:17:10,310 --> 00:17:13,639
She has been the brand
ambassador of Lami and Qin Ya.

256
00:17:13,640 --> 00:17:14,559
After Yu Meiren,

257
00:17:14,560 --> 00:17:16,709
